DATE: 2026-04-30
SUBJECT: feat: major platform update — auth, security, UI, trust score
BODY: Auth:
- 3-step signup: GST verify → Sandbox OTP (tax-payer/otp) → email+password
- GST uniqueness enforced at OTP send; phone uniqueness at OTP verify
- Remove email verification entirely (replaced by GST OTP)
- Suspended users auto-signed-out via AuthContext

Security:
- Rate limiting: OTP 3/10min, verify 5/10min, trade 30/hr, register 5/hr
- CORS locked to ALLOWED_ORIGIN (https://web.dotko.in)
- Security headers: X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, Referrer-Policy
- No hardcoded secrets; all keys via env vars

UI/UX:
- Remove Recent Searches, Quick Access, Score Breakdown
- Add Profile link to Navbar
- ProfileComplete auto-fills from GST data (address, PAN, entity type, mobile)
- Trade form pre-fills submitter info from profile

Trust Score:
- Inactive/Cancelled GST → null score (N/A), not scored
- Proportional deductions: 2 defaults / 10 trades = 10pt, not 60pt
- ScoreRing handles null with gray ring + Inactive badge

Trade & Admin:
- Defaults show red border + DEFAULT badge in TradeTable
- Complaint display fixed: Complainant vs Against columns
- User deletion cascades subcollections (submittedTrades, searches)
- Firestore rules: admin can delete/update user docs
- Timestamps enforced on all writes

